# Custom Workspace Concept

Traditional IDE:

workspace = source code

Industrial Theia:

workspace = operational environment

Example:

Factory A/

```
firmware/
documentation/
training/
maintenance/
procedures/
inventory/
tasks/
```

The workspace becomes the complete representation of an industrial operation.

